'''伊朗清真寺'''（Iranian Mosque，{{lang-ar|المسجد الشيعي الإيراني}}; {{lang-fa|{{Nastaliq|مسجد شیعه ایرانی}}}}）又名'''Ali ibn Abi Talib Iranian Mosque''')是一座伊斯兰教[[什叶派|什叶派]]清真寺，位于[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯联合酋长国]][[迪拜|迪拜]]布尔迪拜区<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dubai360.com/#!s=2041-bur-dubai-textile-souk-outside-iranian-mosque&l=ar|title=Bur Dubai, Textile Souk, outside Iranian Mosque|work=Dubai360|accessdate=2015-07-01|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106143157/https://dubai360.com/#!s=2041-bur-dubai-textile-souk-outside-iranian-mosque&l=ar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。清真寺起源于该市的伊朗社区<ref name="Thomas">{{cite book|last1=Thomas|first1=Gavin|title=Frommer's Dubai and Abu Dhabi Day by Day|date=2003|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9780470684597|page=43|url=https://books.google.com.pk/books?id=-hdMmZk8H5gC&pg=PA43#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate=2015-07-02|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223904/https://books.google.com.pk/books?id=-hdMmZk8H5gC&pg=PA43#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==建筑== 
[[File:Iranian_Shia_Mosque,_Dubai,_UAE_(4324609002).jpg|thumb]]
伊朗清真寺为波斯建筑风格，建筑的内部和外部都是色彩缤纷，其[[立面|立面]]和[[洋葱形圆顶|洋葱形圆顶]]都使用了植物图样的波斯蓝底瓷砖。<ref name="Thomas"/> 

